Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.99,0:01:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.27,0:01:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾沙鲁老师叫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.73,0:02:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说让你赶紧过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:17.03,tm,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,250)}{\fad(1000,0)}约翰之死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多萨纳·阿桑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是约翰叔叔的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天凌晨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父亲多萨纳·约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突发心脏病…去世…了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简短的来信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻描淡写地一笔带过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无情的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…一心就想着照顾比兰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假也没能回去看望他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳 约翰希望你能够好好学习
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰给你留下了这些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真像约翰的作风呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些…都是叔叔教我念过的书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他将那些晦涩的生字用浅显易懂的方法教授给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭了 莫库
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…大叔他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘肯定比你更加难过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁库 莫库 谢谢你们帮我把书搬过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点小事不足挂齿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:04:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有帮忙搬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还不是因为莫库你想在艾琳面前逞英雄么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫库
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我就好好地教你养蜂的知识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会做竖琴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 比兰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾沙鲁老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾沙鲁老师 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰最近挺好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 它很有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾沙鲁老师 我已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要先暂时停止照顾比兰的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以找人代替…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用…不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近过的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托姆鲁学长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:08:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么久没见 你怎么没反应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不欢迎一下什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我给你带礼物来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兽木雕?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用家乡的优质木材做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳 午饭来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的午饭是清爽可口的蔬菜汤和软糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡利沙大婶说我们也可以一起吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰最近如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 它很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:08:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个蔬菜汤真好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己做的 当然会自夸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被识穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不甘心 不过真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先回比兰那里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 要更加努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是应该再多送一只王兽木雕给她啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要为小姑娘多多打气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳她怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,养育的她长大的叔叔去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 和比兰一模一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃…吃掉了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑的连眼泪都流出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托姆鲁学长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 被比兰咬了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个…你很难过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.04,0:11:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我没有精神 比兰会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我必须振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳她似乎在强撑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能为她做点什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 艾沙鲁老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧准备一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要出门去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出门?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.39,0:12:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顾比兰的工作已经拜托给托姆鲁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预计明天晚上可以回来 没有问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去约翰那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这屋子真是够呛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墙壁和褥子都破烂不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该再找个好一点的地方住才对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…明天要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰和我的秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密基地?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于切下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点味道都没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还冷掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不过很久没在宿舍以外的地方吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很新鲜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还有个很大的澡堂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭后咱们去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如传闻所说 真是间不错的澡堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过水质的话 还是卡扎姆的澡堂比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生的那个村庄里也有这样的澡堂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常会和妈妈一起这样泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成长的村子也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个很大的澡堂 常常这样玩耍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我小的时候 真的很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜂蜜?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加进去会很美味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是约翰做的蜂蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 请尝尝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到他会当养蜂人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没想过约翰会从事教导师以外的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他将成绩落后的同学召集到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是给他们补课
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天我问他为什么要特意这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 他这样回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很乐于发现并挖掘人的潜能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟有这种想法的人存在 真让我吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔从以前起就没有变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当听到他说要辞去教导师一职时我非常意外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个天生热爱教学事业的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来我成了一名研究人员要去卡扎姆赴任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 我想起了约翰的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够做挖掘人潜能的工作也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:16:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有约翰的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你也不会像现在这样坐在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有叔叔的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会有人救起来历不明的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,养育我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授我知识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明想着有一天要向叔叔报恩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我却不能回报给他什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要朝着自己的人生之路前进就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想约翰他…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因为有你 才能坚持自己的生存方式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾沙鲁老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请再多告诉我一些叔叔学生时代的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个书虫 会整夜整夜的读书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常会在课堂上打瞌睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还会逃课
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲到秘密基地去学自己喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密基地吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是间搭建在鲜花盛开的草原上的小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个都很喜欢那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他从前很瘦 还蛮帅的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到他的时候 还以为是头熊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 他总会毫不顾忌地放屁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是昨天跟你提过的秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我和约翰充满回忆的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾在这里进行考前复习
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的一点都没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会说"死只不过是回归土地"这种话的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会乖乖地躺在坟墓里的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他一定还在这里的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰是在尽力挖掘自己的潜能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她决心以无愧于约翰的生活方式活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.43,0:22:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 非常感谢您带我来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.81,0:22:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.30,0:24:04.11,xjyg,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为叔叔去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.11,0:24:06.45,xjyg,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳整个人变的很恍惚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.00,0:24:09.81,xjyg,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她还是和比兰很亲密
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.81,0:24:12.57,xjyg,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不像人类和王兽之间的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.96,0:24:16.46,xjyg,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这样下去艾琳应该会渐渐忘却悲伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.95,0:24:21.33,xjyg,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在这个时候却发生了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.94,0:24:23.60,xjyg,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兽之奏者 艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.60,0:24:25.11,xjyg,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兽之牙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.21,0:24:31.00,tm2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,255)}兽之牙


